          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="d-flex size-description">
              <div class="size-chart-specification__content">
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                  This is suitable for all adult-sized mouths.
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                  Ensures a snug, comfortable fit for best effectiveness.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="size-chart__subheading">Mouthpiece Dimensions</div>
            <div class="size-chart__table-wrapper">
