                <tr class="size-chart-table__header">
                  <th>Size</th>
                  <th>Length</th>
                  <th>Width</th>
                  <th>Height</th>
                  <th>Best for</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Medium</td>
                  <td>4.2 cm</td>
                  <td>6.5 cm</td>
                  <td>0.9 cm</td>
                  <td>All adult-sized mouths.</td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="size-chart__subheading">Need help on how to measure?</div>
            <div class="size-chart-specification__content">
              1. Measure Your Mouth Width:
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                Use a soft measuring tape or a ruler.
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                Open your mouth slightly and measure the distance between the outer edges of your molars (back teeth).
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="size-chart-specification__content">
              2. Measure Your Mouth Length:
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                Place the measuring tape from the front of your upper teeth to the back of your molars.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="size-chart-specification__content">
              3. Compare with Our Mouthpiece Dimensions:
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                Medium Size: 4.2 cm (Length) x 6.5 cm (Width) x 0.9 cm (Height)
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="size-chart-specification__dot">○</div>
                If you're between sizes, we recommend going one size up for comfort.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="size-chart__subheading">Already found your fit? Purchase Now</div>
            <div>
              If you're still uncertain about which size to choose, feel free to reach out to me at
              <span class="size-chart__email">ken@getreviv.com</span>.
            </div>
          </div>
